<h1 align="center">MUdaciCards project</h1>

This is the UdaciCards project, a mobile application (Android or iOS - or both) that allows users to study collections of flashcards. 
The project is a mobile app developed with React Native.

## Installation

Clone the repository, cd into directory 'mobile-flashcards', and use yarn install.

## Usage

The project can be run 

- `yarn start`

This will open Expo Developer Tools in the browser. You can then do one of the following.

  Scan the QR Code using the Expo Client app ([Expo Client for Android & iOS](https://expo.io/tools#client)) from an Android or iOS device.

